{% extends "base.twig" %}

{% block content %}
	<main id="show">
        <div class="show-header">
            <div class="bg-image"></div>
            <div class="show-navigation">
                <a href="#" class="prev button inverse">Previous</a>
                <a href="#" class="next button inverse">Next</a>
            </div>
            <div class="content grid">
                <div class="eight column">
                    <h5 class="color-rose-purple">Musical Comedy / Special Shows</h5>
                    <h2 class="color-bloom-red">Cinderella</h2>
                    <p class="meta">Dec 2 - Dec 18</p>
                    <p class="meta">Cantey V. Sutton Theatre (Reserved Seating)</p>
                    <hr class="dash" />
                </div>
                <div class="four column">
                    <a href="#" class="button">Buy Tickets</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="show-content grid">

            <div class="seven column">
            <p>This musical comedy is a holiday sugarplum for the whole family; just the right mixture of comedy and romance to add the sparkle of magic to your holiday season. A visually stunning musical combining elegant costumes and scenery with song, dance, conniving step-relatives and resourceful fairy-folk.</p>

            <p>Based on the fairy tale by Charles Perrault.</p>
            <p>Adaptation and lyrics by Jim Eiler.</p>
            <p>Music by Jim Eiler and Jeanne Bargy.</p>
            <p>Directed by Rod &amp; Nancy Rich.</p>

            <p><strong>In partnership with WRAL, Friday, December 2 is <a href="#">Coats for the Children night</a> at Cinderella! $10 of every ticket goes to provide warm, winter clothing for Salvation Army families in need.</strong></p>

            </div>

            <div class="one column"></div>

            <div class="four column">

                <h4>Ticket Information</h4>

                <p>Tickets available now. Buy them online or from the box office at 919-821-3111. Group sales will also be available from the box office.</p>

                <p>Tickets for Cinderella are also available now as an add-on to a Season Membership - save $6 off a ticket!</p>

                <p>Ticket prices (tax included):</p>

                <ul>
                    <li>First Weekend: $28</li>
                    <li>Members: $27</li>
                    <li>All other tickets: Starting at $33</li>
                </ul>

            </div>
        </div>

        <a class="photo-gallery" href="#">
            <header class="bg-bloom-red">
                <h3 href="#" class="color-white">
                Photo Gallery
                </h3>
            </header>
            <span><h2>View &rarr;</h2></span>
            <div class="grid">
            <div class="four column"></div>
            <div class="four column"></div>
            <div class="four column"></div>
            </div>
        </a>

        <div style="height: 600px;"></div>

        <div class="grid promos">
       
        <a class="six column promo" href="#" style="background-image: url({{ theme.link }}/images/shows/the_whipping_man.jpg);">
            <header>
                <p class="eyebrow">Prev:</p>
                <h3 class="title">The Whipping Man</h3>
            </header>
        </a>

        <a class="six column promo" href="#" style="background-image: url({{ theme.link }}/images/shows/a_piece_of_my_heart.jpg);">
            <header style="position: absolute; right: 0; text-align: right;">
                <p class="eyebrow">Next:</p>
                <h3 class="title">A Piece of My Heart</h3>
            </header>
        </a>

        </div>
    </main>
{% endblock %}